  "source": "[\\empty.set]\nDefines: E is \\set\nexpresses:\n. forAll: x is \\set\n  then:\n  . not: x \"in\" E\nDocumented:\n. called: \"empty set\"\n. written: \"\\emptyset\"\n. description: \"The unique set with no elements, also denoted $\\{\\}$. Its existence is guaranteed by the axiom of the empty set, and its uniqueness by the axiom of extension.\"\nId: \"6953e4a8-96c5-44f5-8c58-b55a02116d4a\"",
